@HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@SaleId = 4f981dc8-3482-411a-8bb7-e0344d5c1920
@ItemId = 5d92df9a-8b3c-4a30-84a1-77d0794939b4

### Create a Sale (with 3 items: 10 items [20% discount], 5 items [10% discount], 2 items [no discount])
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "saleDate": "2026-06-08T16:00:00Z",
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "branchId": "7b8db00e-4fa0-482a-bc96-1a892b1a9f02",
  "branchName": "Main Branch",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "4fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa1",
      "productName": "Beer Case",
      "quantity": 10,
      "unitPrice": 15.0
    },
    {
      "productId": "4fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa2",
      "productName": "Soda Bottle",
      "quantity": 5,
      "unitPrice": 2.5
    },
    {
      "productId": "4fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa3",
      "productName": "Chips Bag",
      "quantity": 2,
      "unitPrice": 3.0
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get Sale by ID
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/sales/{{SaleId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List Sales (with pagination, order, and filters)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/sales?_page=1&_size=10&_order=saleDate desc&customerName=John*
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Sale
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/sales/{{SaleId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "saleDate": "2026-06-08T16:30:00Z",
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "customerName": "John Doe Updated",
  "branchId": "7b8db00e-4fa0-482a-bc96-1a892b1a9f02",
  "branchName": "Main Branch Updated",
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "{{ItemId}}",
      "productId": "4fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa1",
      "productName": "Beer Case",
      "quantity": 12,
      "unitPrice": 14.5
    }
  ]
}

###

### Cancel Sale
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/sales/{{SaleId}}/cancel
Accept: application/json

###

### Cancel Sale Item
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/sales/{{SaleId}}/items/{{ItemId}}/cancel
Accept: application/json

###

### Delete Sale
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/api/sales/{{SaleId}}
Accept: application/json
